Porcini are the boletus mushrooms.

00:23:14.885 --> 00:23:20.120
You know, in Italy, of course,
they are very much prized.

00:23:20.120 --> 00:23:26.120
But dried porcini for me, it's
an essential in my kitchen.

00:23:26.120 --> 00:23:31.060
It is one of the umamis that
