00:26:54.590 --> 00:26:56.880
in there, and give them the flavor.

00:26:56.880 --> 00:26:59.760
So every element has a flavor.

00:26:59.760 --> 00:27:02.390
And then you add them on.

00:27:02.390 --> 00:27:04.730
But I'll add them about halfway through.

00:27:04.730 --> 00:27:09.720
If I wanted to do a shrimp risotto,
shrimps, two, three minutes,

00:27:09.720 --> 00:27:10.940
they're done.

00:27:10.940 --> 00:27:14.120
I would saute them quickly,
also flavor them, and then

00:27:14.120 --> 00:27:18.470
add them in the last two,
three minutes of the risotto

00:27:18.470 --> 00:27:20.730
so that they finish together.

