So be careful, because they do tend
to have a little bit of sand or Earth

00:32:26.410 --> 00:32:29.530
because, you know, they
are from the Earth,

00:32:29.530 --> 00:32:33.470
and the stem usually
maintains some of that.

00:32:33.470 --> 00:32:46.260
So I will-- you can strain it
through a cheesecloth or a clean rag.

00:32:46.260 --> 00:32:53.140
But I will just kind of pour and leave
a teaspoon at the bottom with the dust.

