of pulling out of the starches,

00:35:06.890 --> 00:35:11.480
retaining the kernel whole,
and yet a creamy result.

00:35:11.480 --> 00:35:14.615
Because if I put all of
this, the rice will open up.

00:35:14.615 --> 00:35:15.937
It will open up.

00:35:15.937 --> 00:35:18.020
And I'm sure that you've
had that experience where

00:35:18.020 --> 00:35:20.840
