00:35:20.840 --> 00:35:22.240
it's not cooked yet.

00:35:22.240 --> 00:35:23.930
And that's exactly what happens.

00:35:23.930 --> 00:35:31.010
Too much liquid all at once in the--

00:35:31.010 --> 00:35:31.930
OK.

