of break down in the risotto,

00:37:02.860 --> 00:37:05.340
but I also like to have a little crunch.

00:37:05.340 --> 00:37:07.620
So I split it in half.

00:37:07.620 --> 00:37:13.500
I throw half in like I do the mushroom,
and let that half cook and cook.

00:37:13.500 --> 00:37:17.730
And then the other half that
I want just to remain crunchy.

00:37:17.730 --> 00:37:21.560
So it's a question of,
you know, just timing.

00:37:21.560 --> 00:37:24.225
It's like dancing.

00:37:24.225 --> 00:37:26.640
You do those steps and then
you do the other steps,

00:37:26.640 --> 00:37:28.270
and then together, it looks good.

00:37:28.270 --> 00:37:28.770
So--

00:37:28.770 --> 00:37:30.510
