00:42:02.910 --> 00:42:06.180
because mushrooms absorb
water and are porous.

00:42:06.180 --> 00:42:07.710
So sometimes if you take--

00:42:07.710 --> 00:42:13.770
you cut off the base, the dirt very
well, and then you take a wet towel

00:42:13.770 --> 00:42:17.790
and you clean them off,
usually that works well.

