And if you cook it,
the more you cook it,

00:43:03.080 --> 00:43:05.670
there's a bitterness that comes out.

00:43:05.670 --> 00:43:10.260
That's why you see the
pepper mill on the table.

00:43:10.260 --> 00:43:12.930
It's not because, you
know, initially, oh, they

00:43:12.930 --> 00:43:15.090
want it to look good and serve you.

00:43:15.090 --> 00:43:17.380
It's because it just makes sense.

00:43:17.380 --> 00:43:20.250
You add pepper for maximum.

00:43:20.250 --> 00:43:27.330
And purest flavor of black pepper
is to add it the last minute,

00:43:27.330 --> 00:43:28.680
not to really cook it.

00:43:28.680 --> 00:43:31.860
Maybe a few minutes before,
but not to overly cook it.

00:43:31.860 --> 00:43:37.220
So I have it there, and I'm
going to leave it there.

