are you guys almost there?

00:56:56.230 --> 00:56:57.831
Did you taste the salt?

00:56:57.831 --> 00:57:00.717
[LAUGHTER]

00:57:01.679 --> 00:57:04.565
Yeah?

00:57:04.565 --> 00:57:05.530
OK.

00:57:05.530 --> 00:57:07.120
You will tell me if they didn't.

